// KodexSidebar
// Left navigation sidebar for the Kodex section of the app.
// Provides links to Dashboard, Topics, Graph, Drafts, and Flags, plus
// cross-links back to Onboarding and the main Collab view.
// synced: 2026-03-26T14:00:05Z

navItems is a static array defining each nav entry (path, label, icon SVG).

FUNCTION KodexSidebar() -> JSX                                         EXPORT  [2026-03-26]
  Uses useLocation to get current path.
  Renders each navItem as a React Router Link with active highlight.
  Active check: exact match for /kodex root, startsWith for all others.
  No own header or title — title is rendered in KodexLayout's top bar.
  Footer section contains cross-links to Onboarding, Pseudo, and Collab.

---

FUNCTION isActive(path) -> boolean
  Returns true if location.pathname exactly equals "/kodex" (for the root path),
  or starts with path for all other routes.
